      "title": "Two CEB officers on compulsory leave",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Minister of Power and Energy Kanchana Wijesekera says that the Ceylon Electricity Board (CEB) System Control DGM & System Control Chief Engineer Kudahewa has been placed on compulsory leave for June 9th Power Failure.",
        "The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka (PUCSL) recommended investigations on Power Failure & Operation of Sojitz & Westcoast Power plants out of the schedule incurring a cost of Rs. 320 Mn."
      ],
